-spacing: -.1pt;\"> </span>a<span style=\"letter-spacing: -.15pt;\"> </span>C&acirc;mara<span style=\"letter-spacing: -.1pt;\"> </span>dos<span style=\"letter-spacing: 2.0pt;\"> </span>Deputados um centro de debate das quest&otilde;es relacionadas &agrave; igualdade de g&ecirc;nero e &agrave; defesa<span style=\"letter-spacing: 2.0pt;\"> </span>dos<span style=\"letter-spacing: -.35pt;\"> </span>direitos<span style=\"letter-spacing: -.3pt;\"> </span>das<span style=\"letter-spacing: -.3pt;\"> </span>mulheres<span style=\"letter-spacing: -.3pt;\"> </span>no<span style=\"letter-spacing: -.3pt;\"> </span>Brasil<span style=\"letter-spacing: -.3pt;\"> </span>e<span style=\"letter-spacing: -.3pt;\"> </span>no<span style=\"letter-spacing: -.3pt;\"> </span>mundo.<span style=\"letter-spacing: -.3pt;\"> </span></span><span lang=\"PT\" style=\"font-size: 8.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Source Sans 3 Light\',sans-serif; color: #646363;\">(</span><em style=\"mso-bidi-font-style: normal;\"><span lang=\"PT\" style=\"font-size: 8.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Source Sans 3 Light\',sans-serif; color: #706f6f;\">Caput<span style=\"letter-spacing: -.4pt;\"> </span></span></em><span lang=\"PT\" style=\"font-size: 8.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Source Sans 3 Light\',sans-serif; color: #646363;\">do<span style=\"letter-spacing: -.4pt;\"> </span>artigo<span style=\"letter-spacing: -.4pt;\"> </span>acrescido<span style=\"letter-spacing: -.4pt;\"> </span>pela<span style=\"letter-spacing: -.4pt;\"> </span>Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o<span style=\"letter-spacing: -.4pt;\"> </span>n&ordm;<span style=\"letter-spacing: -.4pt;\"> </span>10<span style=\"letter-spacing: -.4pt;\"> </span>de<span style=\"letter-spacing: -.4pt;\"> </span>2009<span style=\"letter-spacing: -.4pt;\"> </span>e<span style=\"letter-spacing: 2.0pt;\"> </span>com reda&ccedil;&atilde;o dada pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 31 de 2013)</span></p>'),(24,2,11,NULL,NULL,'Art. 20-